      "bookSlug": "first-corinthians",
      "chapterNumber": 7,
      "verseNumber": 6,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Corinthians 7:6",
      "text": "ܗܕܐ ܕܝܢ ܐܡܪ ܐܢܐ ܐܝܟ ܕܠܡܚܝܠܐ ܠܘ ܡܢ ܦܘܩܕܢܐ ܀",
